<h4>Get an additional $30 rebate when you purchase a new ENERGY STAR® certified dehumidifier!</h4>
<img alt="Energy Star" src="./files/my-energy-star.gif" style="float: left; padding: 3px;" onclick="javascript:ga(&#39;create&#39;, &#39;UA-5856712-1&#39;, &#39;auto&#39;, &#39;marketsegmentTracker&#39;);javascript:ga(&#39;marketsegmentTracker.send&#39;, &#39;event&#39;, marketsegment, &#39;download&#39;, &#39;my-energy-star&#39;);" title="Energy star approved logo.">
<p>An ENERGY STAR certified dehumidifier can save you more than $300 in energy costs over the life of the unit! Mass Save is offering an additional $30 rebate for purchasing an ENERGY STAR certified model. Now that's a lot of savings! For more information on ENERGY STAR certified dehumidifiers, the benefits of purchasing them, as well as how you can receive an additional $30 rebate, visit our <a href="http://www.masssave.com/en/residential/lighting-and-appliances/appliances/dehumidifiers/">Dehumidifiers</a> page.</p>
<h4>Eligibility</h4>
<p>These offers are only open to Massachusetts residential electric customers of Cape Light Compact, Eversource Energy, National Grid or Unitil. Dehumidifiers must be turned in at a designated turn-in event between 4/1/2017 – 10/31/2017, and rebate requests for these units must be postmarked or submitted online by 11/30/2017. To receive an additional $30 rebate, you must purchase a qualifying dehumidifier between 1/1/2017 – 12/31/2017. Rebate requests for new dehumidifiers must be postmarked or submitted online by 1/31/2018.</p>
